{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal to share someone's criminal convictions on social media",
        "additional_details": "In today's world with the rise of social media it is too easy for people to cause harm by sharing sensitive information, including about a person's criminal convictions.\r\n \r\nOnce this information is on social media it can cause significant harm. We believe this should be made illegal.\r\n",
        "background": "No one should be allowed to share details of anyone's convictions for criminal offences on any social media outlet as this can cause harm or harassment and even incite vigilantism.",
